                        </div></div>
                    <p id="4">Одиночные SMS отправляются моментально.Массовые отправки ставятся в очередь и отправляются на платформы операторов каждую минуту. Отчёт о доставке обновляется на протяжении 7 суток.</p>

                    <h3 style="font-size: 28px; color: #636363; padding-top: 20px;">Available options</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>customer name: [customer_name] - wil be truncated to 10 chars</li>
                        <li>customer last name: [customer_second_name]  - wil be truncated to 10 chars</li>
                        <li>customer email: [customer_email] - attention, value length is not trimmed</li>
                        <li>customer phone: [customer_phone] - will return clean phone number, digits only</li>
                        <li>game date: [game_date] - format DD.MM.YYYY</li>
                        <li>game time: [game_time] - format HH:MM</li>
                        <li>game price: [game_price] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                        <li>room title: [room_title] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                        <li>room city: [room_city] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                        <li>room address: [room_address] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                        <li>room phone: [room_phone] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                        <li>room email: [room_email] - length depends on the administrator-defined value</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p><b>* <span style="color: red">BE CAREFUL!</span></b> Options with [customer_*] prefix are entered by customer
                    and they are can have unexpected length of value.
                    Because of it messages could be more expensive than expected.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
